folder: Matthews Avenue & Rhinelander Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Matthews Avenue, east side, north from Rhinelander to Bronxdale Avenues. The house in the center is number 1913 Bronxdale Avenue.

June 22, 1940

P. L. Sperr

folder: Rhinelander Avenue & Matthews Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Rhinelander Avenue, north side, between Matthews and Muliner Avenues, showing a very old dwelling, partly made out of stone and partly out of wood. It was at one time on the B. Downing property.
June 22, 1940
Views 1, 2, 3
P.L. Sperr
